## ğŸ›ï¸ 4. **Prompt Generation Controls â€“ Temperature, Top-p, Top-k**

### ğŸ”¥ **Temperature**
- Range: 0 â†’ 1 (creativity vs accuracy)
  - 0 = deterministic
  - >0.7 = creative (but prone to hallucination)

### ğŸ² **Top-p (nucleus sampling)**
- p = cumulative probability  
  - p=0.5 â†’ safer, focused  
  - p=1.0 â†’ all tokens considered (high diversity, low control)

### ğŸ§® **Top-k**
- k = number of top tokens to sample from  
  - k=0 / -1 = disable top-k (all tokens considered)
  - Higher k = more randomness

> âœ… Cohere default: `top-k=0`  
> âœ… Meta Llama default: `top-k=-1`

